OL,5, Teachers have been urged to warn pupils
OL,6, against the dangers of sextortion, a   
OL,7, form of blackmail involving threats    
OL,8, that intimate pictures will be shared. 
OL,10,FThe National Crime Agency (NCA) sent   
OL,11,Fthe "unprecedented" alert to teachers  
OL,12,Fon Monday after cases surged worldwide.
OL,14,FRos Dowey's son Murray died by suicide 
OL,15,Fafter he was tricked into sending      
OL,16,Fcompromising pictures by criminals     
OL,17,Fposing as a girl online.               
OL,19,F"They've totally destroyed our family,"
OL,20,FMrs Dowey told the BBC.                
